"""AutoLogin — magic-link tokens for the tests-360 pattern.

ONLY generated when ``module-autologin-tests360`` is selected. This module
is the EXPLICIT EXCEPTION to the rule "GET must not mutate state": the
tests-360 product uses GET-able magic links for passwordless login from
emails and chat tools that strip POST bodies.

The token endpoint REQUIRES a valid signed token in the URL; without it
the view 404s. Without the module active, no such endpoint exists at all.

Anti-pattern avoided (inpacto-ghl-integrations audit): the original tests-360
exposed a GET endpoint that auto-logged in WITHOUT a token. Here we
require the signed token AND mark it used atomically.
"""

default_app_config = "apps.accounts.autologin.apps.AutoLoginConfig"